      "title": "Slime Egg",
      "pageid": 3293,
      "text": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><div id=\"infoboxborder\">\n<table id=\"infoboxtable\">\n<tbody><tr>\n\t<td colspan=\"2\" id=\"infoboxheader\">Slime Egg</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n\t<td colspan=\"2\" style=\"padding-bottom: 5px; text-align: center;\"><a href=\"/File:Green_Slime_Egg.png\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"Green Slime Egg.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/1/1d/Green_Slime_Egg.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"48\" height=\"48\" /></a>&#160;<a href=\"/File:Blue_Slime_Egg.png\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"Blue Slime Egg.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/a/a2/Blue_Slime_Egg.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"48\" height=\"48\" /></a>&#160;<a href=\"/File:Red_Slime_Egg.png\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"Red Slime Egg.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/a/ae/Red_Slime_Egg.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"48\" height=\"48\" /></a>&#160;<a href=\"/File:Purple_Slime_Egg.png\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"Purple Slime Egg.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/6/65/Purple_Slime_Egg.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"48\" height=\"48\" /></a>&#160;<a href=\"/File:Tiger_Slime_Egg.png\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"Tiger Slime Egg.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/1/1f/Tiger_Slime_Egg.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"48\" height=\"48\" /></a></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n\t<td colspan=\"2\" id=\"infoboxdetail\" style=\"text-align: center; font-style: italic; padding-right: 3px;\">Can be hatched in a slime incubator.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n\t<td colspan=\"2\" id=\"infoboxsection\" style=\"text-align: center; padding-left: 0; padding-right: 0;\">Information</td>\n</tr>\n\n\t<tr>\n\t\t<td id=\"infoboxsection\">Source</td>\n\t\t<td id=\"infoboxdetail\">\n<ul><li><a href=\"/Slime_Egg-Press\" title=\"Slime Egg-Press\">Slime Egg-Press</a></li>\n<li>Drop from <a href=\"/Slimes\" title=\"Slimes\">Slimes</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/Slimejack\" title=\"Slimejack\">Slimejack</a> / <a href=\"/Lionfish\" title=\"Lionfish\">Lionfish</a> <a href=\"/Fish_Pond\" title=\"Fish Pond\">Fish Pond</a></li></ul></td>\n\t</tr>\n\t<tr>\n\t\t<td id=\"infoboxsection\">Energy</td>\n\t\t\t<td id=\"infoboxdetail\"><i>Inedible</i></td> \n\t</tr><tr>\n\t<td id=\"infoboxsection\">Sell Price</td>\n\t\t<td id=\"infoboxdetail\">\n<p><img alt=\"Green Slime Egg.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/1/1d/Green_Slime_Egg.png/24px-Green_Slime_Egg.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/1/1d/Green_Slime_Egg.png/36px-Green_Slime_Egg.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/1/1d/Green_Slime_Egg.png 2x\" /> 1,000g\n<br /><img alt=\"Blue Slime Egg.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/a/a2/Blue_Slime_Egg.png/24px-Blue_Slime_Egg.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/a/a2/Blue_Slime_Egg.png/36px-Blue_Slime_Egg.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/a/a2/Blue_Slime_Egg.png 2x\" /> 1,750g\n<br /><img alt=\"Red Slime Egg.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/a/ae/Red_Slime_Egg.png/24px-Red_Slime_Egg.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/a/ae/Red_Slime_Egg.png/36px-Red_Slime_Egg.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/a/ae/Red_Slime_Egg.png 2x\" /> 2,500g\n<br /><img alt=\"Purple Slime Egg.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/6/65/Purple_Slime_Egg.png/24px-Purple_Slime_Egg.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/6/65/Purple_Slime_Egg.png/36px-Purple_Slime_Egg.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/6/65/Purple_Slime_Egg.png 2x\" /> 5,000g\n<br /><img alt=\"Tiger Slime Egg.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/1/1f/Tiger_Slime_Egg.png/24px-Tiger_Slime_Egg.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/1/1f/Tiger_Slime_Egg.png/36px-Tiger_Slime_Egg.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/1/1f/Tiger_Slime_Egg.png 2x\" /> 8,000g\n</p>\n\t\t</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table>\n</div>\n<p><b>Slime Eggs</b> can be obtained as rare drops from <a href=\"/Slimes\" title=\"Slimes\">slimes</a> or by putting 100 <a href=\"/Slime\" title=\"Slime\">slime</a> into a <a href=\"/Slime_Egg-Press\" title=\"Slime Egg-Press\">Slime Egg-Press</a>. Purple and red Slime Eggs can also be found in <a href=\"/Skull_Cavern#Treasure_Rooms\" title=\"Skull Cavern\">treasure rooms</a> in the Skull Cavern. One Green Slime Egg may be produced daily in a <a href=\"/Slimejack\" title=\"Slimejack\">Slimejack</a> <a href=\"/Fish_Pond\" title=\"Fish Pond\">Fish Pond</a> when the population of the pond reaches 9. A Tiger Slime Egg might drop when a <a href=\"/Slimes\" title=\"Slimes\">Tiger Slime</a> is killed in the <a href=\"/Volcano_Dungeon\" title=\"Volcano Dungeon\">Volcano Dungeon</a> or West area of <a href=\"/Ginger_Island\" title=\"Ginger Island\">Ginger Island</a>. One Tiger Slime Egg may be produced daily in a <a href=\"/Lionfish\" title=\"Lionfish\">Lionfish</a> <a href=\"/Fish_Pond\" title=\"Fish Pond\">Fish Pond</a> when the population of the pond reaches 9.\n</p><p>The color of egg produced from a Slime Egg-Press is random. There is a 5% chance the egg will be purple, 9.5% chance of red, 21.375% chance of blue, and 64.125% chance of green.<sup id=\"cite_ref-eggcolor_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-eggcolor-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>Once a <a href=\"/Slime_Hutch\" title=\"Slime Hutch\">Slime Hutch</a> is built on <a href=\"/The_Farm\" title=\"The Farm\">the Farm</a>, there is a 1% chance that a slime (encountered anywhere) will drop a Slime Egg when slain. Green slimes drop green eggs, blue slimes drop blue eggs, red slimes drop red eggs, purple slimes drop purple eggs, and tiger slimes drop tiger slime eggs.\n</p><p>Slime Eggs can be sold at different prices depending on the color, or placed in a <a href=\"/Slime_Incubator\" title=\"Slime Incubator\">Slime Incubator</a>.\n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\" role=\"navigation\" aria-labelledby=\"mw-toc-heading\"><input type=\"checkbox\" role=\"button\" id=\"toctogglecheckbox\" class=\"toctogglecheckbox\" style=\"display:none\" /><div class=\"toctitle\" lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\"><h2 id=\"mw-toc-heading\">Contents</h2><span class=\"toctogglespan\"><label class=\"toctogglelabel\" for=\"toctogglecheckbox\"></label></span></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Incubation\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Incubation</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#Gifting\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Gifting</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#Bundles\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Bundles</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#Tailoring\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Tailoring</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-5\"><a href=\"#Quests\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">5</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Quests</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-6\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">6</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-7\"><a href=\"#History\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">7</span> <span class=\"toctext\">History</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Incubation\">Incubation</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/mediawiki/index.php?title=Slime_Egg&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" title=\"Edit section: Incubation\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>The Slime egg can be hatched into a slime in a <a href=\"/Slime_Incubator\" title=\"Slime Incubator\">Slime Incubator</a>. The incubation takes 4000 minutes in game time, which amounts to 3 entire days (6 am to 2 am) and 6 hours.  The <a href=\"/Farming#Farming_Skill\" title=\"Farming\">Coopmaster Profession</a> cuts this time in half. \n</p><p>Green eggs will hatch green slimes, blue eggs hatch blue slimes, red eggs hatch red slimes, purple eggs hatch purple slimes, and tiger eggs hatch tiger slimes.\n</p><p>The gender of the egg is completely random and can't be found out before hatching the egg.\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Gifting\">Gifting</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/mediawiki/index.php?title=Slime_Egg&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" title=\"Edit section: Gifting\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<table class=\"wikitable roundedborder\">\n<tbody><tr>\n<th colspan=\"2\">Villager Reactions\n<p class=\"mw-empty-elt\">\n</p>\n</th></tr>\n<tr>\n<th>Hate\n</th>\n<td><span class=\"no-wrap\"><a href=\"/Abigail\" title=\"Abigail\"><img alt=\"Abigail Icon.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/6/63/Abigail_Icon.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\" /></a>&#160;<a href=\"/Abigail\" title=\"Abigail\">Abigail</a></span> • <span class=\"no-wrap\"><a href=\"/Alex\" title=\"Alex\"><img alt=\"Alex Icon.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/7/73/Alex_Icon.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\" /></a>&#160;<a href=\"/Alex\" title=\"Alex\">Alex</a></span> • <span class=\"no-wrap\"><a href=\"/Caroline\" title=\"Caroline\"><img alt=\"Caroline Icon.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/d/d4/Caroline_Icon.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\" /></a>&#160;<a href=\"/Caroline\" title=\"Caroline\">Caroline</a></span> • <span class=\"no-wrap\"><a href=\"/Clint\" title=\"Clint\"><img alt=\"Clint Icon.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/7/74/Clint_Icon.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\" /></a>&#160;<a href=\"/Clint\" title=\"Clint\">Clint</a></span> • <span class=\"no-wrap\"><a href=\"/Demetrius\" title=\"Demetrius\"><img alt=\"Demetrius Icon.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/0/0b/Demetrius_Icon.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\" /></a>&#160;<a href=\"/Demetrius\" title=\"Demetrius\">Demetrius</a></span> • <span class=\"no-wrap\"><a href=\"/Dwarf\" title=\"Dwarf\"><img alt=\"Dwarf Icon.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/0/08/Dwarf_Icon.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\" /></a>&#160;<a href=\"/Dwarf\" title=\"Dwarf\">Dwarf</a></span> • <span class=\"no-wrap\"><a href=\"/Elliott\" title=\"Elliott\"><img alt=\"Elliott Icon.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/6/6f/Elliott_Icon.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\" /></a>&#160;<a href=\"/Elliott\" title=\"Elliott\">Elliott</a></span> • <span class=\"no-wrap\"><a href=\"/Emily\" title=\"Emily\"><img alt=\"Emily Icon.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/c/c3/Emily_Icon.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\" /></a>&#160;<a href=\"/Emily\" title=\"Emily\">Emily</a></span> • <span class=\"no-wrap\"><a href=\"/Evelyn\" title=\"Evelyn\"><img alt=\"Evelyn Icon.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/5/54/Evelyn_Icon.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\" /></a>&#160;<a href=\"/Evelyn\" title=\"Evelyn\">Evelyn</a></span> • <span class=\"no-wrap\"><a href=\"/George\" title=\"George\"><img alt=\"George Icon.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/a/ad/George_Icon.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\" /></a>&#160;<a href=\"/George\" title=\"George\">George</a></span> • <span class=\"no-wrap\"><a href=\"/Gus\" title=\"Gus\"><img alt=\"Gus Icon.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/d/db/Gus_Icon.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\" /></a>&#160;<a href=\"/Gus\" title=\"Gus\">Gus</a></span> • <span class=\"no-wrap\"><a href=\"/Haley\" title=\"Haley\"><img alt=\"Haley Icon.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/f/f7/Haley_Icon.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\" /></a>&#160;<a href=\"/Haley\" title=\"Haley\">Haley</a></span> • <span class=\"no-wrap\"><a href=\"/Harvey\" title=\"Harvey\"><img alt=\"Harvey Icon.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/7/7a/Harvey_Icon.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\" /></a>&#160;<a href=\"/Harvey\" title=\"Harvey\">Harvey</a></span> • <span class=\"no-wrap\"><a href=\"/Jas\" title=\"Jas\"><img alt=\"Jas Icon.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/6/68/Jas_Icon.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\" /></a>&#160;<a href=\"/Jas\" title=\"Jas\">Jas</a></span> • <span class=\"no-wrap\"><a href=\"/Jodi\" title=\"Jodi\"><img alt=\"Jodi Icon.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/f/f7/Jodi_Icon.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\" /></a>&#160;<a href=\"/Jodi\" title=\"Jodi\">Jodi</a></span> • <span class=\"no-wrap\"><a href=\"/Kent\" title=\"Kent\"><img alt=\"Kent Icon.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/8/86/Kent_Icon.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\" /></a>&#160;<a href=\"/Kent\" title=\"Kent\">Kent</a></span> • <span class=\"no-wrap\"><a href=\"/Krobus\" title=\"Krobus\"><img alt=\"Krobus Icon.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/1/10/Krobus_Icon.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\" /></a>&#160;<a href=\"/Krobus\" title=\"Krobus\">Krobus</a></span> • <span class=\"no-wrap\"><a href=\"/Leah\" title=\"Leah\"><img alt=\"Leah Icon.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/6/6e/Leah_Icon.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\" /></a>&#160;<a href=\"/Leah\" title=\"Leah\">Leah</a></span> • <span class=\"no-wrap\"><a href=\"/Leo\" title=\"Leo\"><img alt=\"Leo Icon.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/3/3d/Leo_Icon.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\" /></a>&#160;<a href=\"/Leo\" title=\"Leo\">Leo</a></span> • <span class=\"no-wrap\"><a href=\"/Lewis\" title=\"Lewis\"><img alt=\"Lewis Icon.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/b/b6/Lewis_Icon.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\" /></a>&#160;<a href=\"/Lewis\" title=\"Lewis\">Lewis</a></span> • <span class=\"no-wrap\"><a href=\"/Linus\" title=\"Linus\"><img alt=\"Linus Icon.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/d/db/Linus_Icon.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\" /></a>&#160;<a href=\"/Linus\" title=\"Linus\">Linus</a></span> • <span class=\"no-wrap\"><a href=\"/Marnie\" title=\"Marnie\"><img alt=\"Marnie Icon.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/d/d4/Marnie_Icon.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\" /></a>&#160;<a href=\"/Marnie\" title=\"Marnie\">Marnie</a></span> • <span class=\"no-wrap\"><a href=\"/Maru\" title=\"Maru\"><img alt=\"Maru Icon.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/2/23/Maru_Icon.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\" /></a>&#160;<a href=\"/Maru\" title=\"Maru\">Maru</a></span> • <span class=\"no-wrap\"><a href=\"/Pam\" title=\"Pam\"><img alt=\"Pam Icon.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/b/b6/Pam_Icon.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\" /></a>&#160;<a href=\"/Pam\" title=\"Pam\">Pam</a></span> • <span class=\"no-wrap\"><a href=\"/Penny\" title=\"Penny\"><img alt=\"Penny Icon.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/b/bc/Penny_Icon.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\" /></a>&#160;<a href=\"/Penny\" title=\"Penny\">Penny</a></span> • <span class=\"no-wrap\"><a href=\"/Pierre\" title=\"Pierre\"><img alt=\"Pierre Icon.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/c/cf/Pierre_Icon.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\" /></a>&#160;<a href=\"/Pierre\" title=\"Pierre\">Pierre</a></span> • <span class=\"no-wrap\"><a href=\"/Robin\" title=\"Robin\"><img alt=\"Robin Icon.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/d/d1/Robin_Icon.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\" /></a>&#160;<a href=\"/Robin\" title=\"Robin\">Robin</a></span> • <span class=\"no-wrap\"><a href=\"/Sam\" title=\"Sam\"><img alt=\"Sam Icon.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/5/52/Sam_Icon.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\" /></a>&#160;<a href=\"/Sam\" title=\"Sam\">Sam</a></span> • <span class=\"no-wrap\"><a href=\"/Sandy\" title=\"Sandy\"><img alt=\"Sandy Icon.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/7/7d/Sandy_Icon.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\" /></a>&#160;<a href=\"/Sandy\" title=\"Sandy\">Sandy</a></span> • <span class=\"no-wrap\"><a href=\"/Sebastian\" title=\"Sebastian\"><img alt=\"Sebastian Icon.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/6/6a/Sebastian_Icon.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\" /></a>&#160;<a href=\"/Sebastian\" title=\"Sebastian\">Sebastian</a></span> • <span class=\"no-wrap\"><a href=\"/Shane\" title=\"Shane\"><img alt=\"Shane Icon.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/b/b4/Shane_Icon.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\" /></a>&#160;<a href=\"/Shane\" title=\"Shane\">Shane</a></span> • <span class=\"no-wrap\"><a href=\"/Vincent\" title=\"Vincent\"><img alt=\"Vincent Icon.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/0/0b/Vincent_Icon.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\" /></a>&#160;<a href=\"/Vincent\" title=\"Vincent\">Vincent</a></span> • <span class=\"no-wrap\"><a href=\"/Willy\" title=\"Willy\"><img alt=\"Willy Icon.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/7/73/Willy_Icon.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\" /></a>&#160;<a href=\"/Willy\" title=\"Willy\">Willy</a></span> • <span class=\"no-wrap\"><a href=\"/Wizard\" title=\"Wizard\"><img alt=\"Wizard Icon.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/e/e9/Wizard_Icon.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\" /></a>&#160;<a href=\"/Wizard\" title=\"Wizard\">Wizard</a></span>\n</td></tr></tbody></table>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Bundles\">Bundles</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/mediawiki/index.php?title=Slime_Egg&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" title=\"Edit section: Bundles\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>Slime Egg is not used in any <a href=\"/Bundles\" title=\"Bundles\">bundles</a>.\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Tailoring\">Tailoring</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/mediawiki/index.php?title=Slime_Egg&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" title=\"Edit section: Tailoring\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>Slime Egg is used in the spool of the <a href=\"/2_Willow_Lane#Sewing_Machine\" title=\"2 Willow Lane\">Sewing Machine</a> to create the dyeable <a href=\"/Tailoring#Pants\" title=\"Tailoring\">Baggy Pants</a>. <a href=\"/File:Baggy_Pants.png\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"Baggy Pants.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/2/26/Baggy_Pants.png/36px-Baggy_Pants.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"36\" height=\"36\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/2/26/Baggy_Pants.png 1.5x\" /></a>\nSlime Eggs can also be used as a <a href=\"/Dyeing\" title=\"Dyeing\">dye</a> in the dye pots located in <a href=\"/Haley\" title=\"Haley\">Haley</a>'s and <a href=\"/Emily\" title=\"Emily\">Emily</a>'s house, <a href=\"/2_Willow_Lane\" title=\"2 Willow Lane\">2 Willow Lane</a>. The dye pots the eggs go into match their color, as follows:\n</p>\n<ul><li>Green Slime Eggs are a green dye</li>\n<li>Blue Slime Eggs are a blue dye</li>\n<li>Red Slime Eggs are a red dye</li>\n<li>Purple Slime Eggs are a purple dye</li>\n<li>Tiger Slime Eggs are an orange dye</li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Quests\">Quests</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/mediawiki/index.php?title=Slime_Egg&amp;action=edit&amp;section=5\" title=\"Edit section: Quests\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>The Slime Egg is not used in any <a href=\"/Quests\" title=\"Quests\">quests</a>.\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/mediawiki/index.php?title=Slime_Egg&amp;action=edit&amp;section=6\" title=\"Edit section: References\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-eggcolor-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-eggcolor_1-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\">See <samp>Object::performObjectDropInAction</samp> in the game code.</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"History\">History</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/mediawiki/index.php?title=Slime_Egg&amp;action=edit&amp;section=7\" title=\"Edit section: History\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li><a href=\"/Version_History#1.0\" title=\"Version History\">1.0</a>: Introduced.</li>\n<li><a href=\"/Version_History#1.11\" title=\"Version History\">1.11</a>: Increased sell price for all eggs.</li>\n<li><a href=\"/Version_History#1.4\" title=\"Version History\">1.4</a>: Can now be used in <a href=\"/Tailoring\" title=\"Tailoring\">Tailoring</a>. Can be produced by <a href=\"/Fish_Pond\" title=\"Fish Pond\">Fish Ponds</a>.</li>\n<li><a href=\"/Version_History#1.5\" title=\"Version History\">1.5</a>: Added Tiger Slime Eggs.</li></ul>\n<table class=\"wikitable\" id=\"navbox\">\n<tbody><tr>\n<th colspan=\"2\"><a href=\"/Animals\" title=\"Animals\">Animals</a> and Produce\n</th></tr>\n<tr>\n<th><a href=\"/Coop\" title=\"Coop\">Coop</a>\n</th>\n<td><a href=\"/Chicken\" title=\"Chicken\">Chicken</a> <sup>(<a href=\"/Egg\" title=\"Egg\">Egg</a> • <a href=\"/Large_Egg\" title=\"Large Egg\">Large Egg</a> • <a href=\"/Egg\" title=\"Egg\">Brown Egg</a> • <a href=\"/Large_Egg\" title=\"Large Egg\">Large Brown Egg</a>)</sup> • <a href=\"/Dinosaur\" title=\"Dinosaur\">Dinosaur</a> <sup>(<a href=\"/Dinosaur_Egg\" title=\"Dinosaur Egg\">Dinosaur Egg</a>)</sup> • <a href=\"/Duck\" title=\"Duck\">Duck</a> <sup>(<a href=\"/Duck_Egg\" title=\"Duck Egg\">Duck Egg</a> • <a href=\"/Duck_Feather\" title=\"Duck Feather\">Duck Feather</a>)</sup> • <a href=\"/Golden_Chicken\" title=\"Golden Chicken\">Golden Chicken</a> <sup>(<a href=\"/Golden_Egg\" title=\"Golden Egg\">Golden Egg</a>)</sup> • <a href=\"/Rabbit\" title=\"Rabbit\">Rabbit</a> <sup>(<a href=\"/Wool\" title=\"Wool\">Wool</a> • <a href=\"/Rabbit%27s_Foot\" title=\"Rabbit&#39;s Foot\">Rabbit's Foot</a>)</sup> • <a href=\"/Void_Chicken\" title=\"Void Chicken\">Void Chicken</a> <sup>(<a href=\"/Void_Egg\" title=\"Void Egg\">Void Egg</a>)</sup>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<th><a href=\"/Barn\" title=\"Barn\">Barn</a>\n</th>\n<td><a href=\"/Cow\" title=\"Cow\">Cow</a> <sup>(<a href=\"/Milk\" title=\"Milk\">Milk</a> • <a href=\"/Large_Milk\" title=\"Large Milk\">Large Milk</a>)</sup> • <a href=\"/Goat\" title=\"Goat\">Goat</a> <sup>(<a href=\"/Goat_Milk\" title=\"Goat Milk\">Goat Milk</a> • <a href=\"/Large_Goat_Milk\" title=\"Large Goat Milk\">Large Goat Milk</a>)</sup> • <a href=\"/Sheep\" title=\"Sheep\">Sheep</a>  <sup>(<a href=\"/Wool\" title=\"Wool\">Wool</a>)</sup> • <a href=\"/Ostrich\" title=\"Ostrich\">Ostrich</a> <sup>(<a href=\"/Ostrich_Egg\" title=\"Ostrich Egg\">Ostrich Egg</a>)</sup> • <a href=\"/Pig\" title=\"Pig\">Pig</a> <sup>(<a href=\"/Truffle\" title=\"Truffle\">Truffle</a>)</sup>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<th><a href=\"/Fish_Pond\" title=\"Fish Pond\">Fish Pond</a>\n</th>\n<td><a href=\"/Fish\" title=\"Fish\">Fish</a> <sup>(<a href=\"/Roe\" title=\"Roe\">Roe</a>)</sup>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<th class=\"no-wrap\"><a href=\"/Slime_Hutch\" title=\"Slime Hutch\">Slime Hutch</a>\n</th>\n<td><a href=\"/Slimes\" title=\"Slimes\">Slimes</a> <sup>(<a href=\"/Slime\" title=\"Slime\">Slime</a> • <a href=\"/Slime_Ball\" title=\"Slime Ball\">Slime Ball</a> • <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Slime Egg</a>)</sup>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<th>Other\n</th>\n<td><a href=\"/Animals#Cat_or_Dog\" title=\"Animals\">Cat</a> • <a href=\"/Animals#Cat_or_Dog\" title=\"Animals\">Dog</a> • <a href=\"/Animals#Horse\" title=\"Animals\">Horse</a> • <a href=\"/Animals#Additional_Pets\" title=\"Animals\">Turtle</a>\n</td></tr>\n</tbody></table>\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260414143305\nCache expiry: 86400\nDynamic content: false\nComplications: []\nCPU time usage: 0.127 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.148 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 1173/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 17152/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 2809/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 13/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\nUnstrip recursion depth: 0/20\nUnstrip post‐expand size: 390/5000000 bytes\nLua time usage: 0.004/7.000 seconds\nLua memory usage: 519 KB/50 MB\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%   67.324      1 -total\n 57.46%   38.685      1 Template:Infobox\n 29.16%   19.631      1 Template:Description\n 26.43%   17.792      1 Template:GiftsByItem\n  7.67%    5.164      4 Template:History\n  4.75%    3.196      4 Template:Version\n  4.66%    3.135      1 Template:Price\n  2.85%    1.919      1 Template:InfoboxSEO\n  2.70%    1.821      1 Template:NavboxAnimals\n-->\n\n<!-- Saved in parser cache with key enwiki:pcache:idhash:3293-0!canonical and timestamp 20260414143305 and revision id 182059\n -->\n</div>",
      "wikitext": "{{Infobox\n|eng         = Green Slime Egg\n|image2      = Blue Slime Egg\n|image3      = Red Slime Egg\n|image4      = Purple Slime Egg\n|image5      = Tiger Slime Egg\n|source      = <nowiki/>\n*[[Slime Egg-Press]]\n*Drop from [[Slimes]]\n*[[Slimejack]] / [[Lionfish]] [[Fish Pond]]\n|edibility   = -300\n|quality     = false\n|sellprice   = <nowiki/>\n[[File:Green Slime Egg.png|24px|link=]] 1,000g\n<br />[[File:Blue Slime Egg.png|24px|link=]] 1,750g\n<br />[[File:Red Slime Egg.png|24px|link=]] 2,500g\n<br />[[File:Purple Slime Egg.png|24px|link=]] 5,000g\n<br />[[File:Tiger Slime Egg.png|24px|link=]] 8,000g\n}}\n'''Slime Eggs''' can be obtained as rare drops from [[slimes]] or by putting 100 [[slime]] into a [[Slime Egg-Press]]. Purple and red Slime Eggs can also be found in [[Skull Cavern#Treasure Rooms|treasure rooms]] in the Skull Cavern. One Green Slime Egg may be produced daily in a [[Slimejack]] [[Fish Pond]] when the population of the pond reaches 9. A Tiger Slime Egg might drop when a [[Slimes|Tiger Slime]] is killed in the [[Volcano Dungeon]] or West area of [[Ginger Island]]. One Tiger Slime Egg may be produced daily in a [[Lionfish]] [[Fish Pond]] when the population of the pond reaches 9.\n\nThe color of egg produced from a Slime Egg-Press is random. There is a 5% chance the egg will be purple, 9.5% chance of red, 21.375% chance of blue, and 64.125% chance of green.<ref name=\"eggcolor\"/>\n\nOnce a [[Slime Hutch]] is built on [[the Farm]], there is a 1% chance that a slime (encountered anywhere) will drop a Slime Egg when slain. Green slimes drop green eggs, blue slimes drop blue eggs, red slimes drop red eggs, purple slimes drop purple eggs, and tiger slimes drop tiger slime eggs.\n\nSlime Eggs can be sold at different prices depending on the color, or placed in a [[Slime Incubator]].\n\n==Incubation==\nThe Slime egg can be hatched into a slime in a [[Slime Incubator]]. The incubation takes 4000 minutes in game time, which amounts to 3 entire days (6 am to 2 am) and 6 hours.  The [[Farming#Farming Skill|Coopmaster Profession]] cuts this time in half. \n\nGreen eggs will hatch green slimes, blue eggs hatch blue slimes, red eggs hatch red slimes, purple eggs hatch purple slimes, and tiger eggs hatch tiger slimes.\n\nThe gender of the egg is completely random and can't be found out before hatching the egg.\n\n==Gifting==\n{{GiftsByItem|hate=Robin,Demetrius,Linus,Leo,Pam,Jodi,Kent,Leah,Shane,Elliott,Harvey,Sandy, Maru,Sebastian,Pierre,Caroline,Alex,George,Evelyn,Lewis,Clint,Penny,Emily,Sam,Marnie,Gus,Dwarf,Wizard,Willy,Krobus,Abigail,Haley,Jas,Vincent}}\n\n==Bundles==\nSlime Egg is not used in any [[bundles]].\n\n==Tailoring==\nSlime Egg is used in the spool of the [[2 Willow Lane#Sewing Machine|Sewing Machine]] to create the dyeable [[Tailoring#Pants|Baggy Pants]]. [[File:Baggy Pants.png|36px]]\nSlime Eggs can also be used as a [[Dyeing|dye]] in the dye pots located in [[Haley]]'s and [[Emily]]'s house, [[2 Willow Lane]]. The dye pots the eggs go into match their color, as follows:\n*Green Slime Eggs are a green dye\n*Blue Slime Eggs are a blue dye\n*Red Slime Eggs are a red dye\n*Purple Slime Eggs are a purple dye\n*Tiger Slime Eggs are an orange dye\n\n==Quests==\nThe Slime Egg is not used in any [[quests]].\n\n==References==\n<references>\n<ref name=\"eggcolor\">See <samp>Object::performObjectDropInAction</samp> in the game code.</ref>\n</references>\n\n==History==\n{{History|1.0|Introduced.}}\n{{History|1.11|Increased sell price for all eggs.}}\n{{History|1.4|Can now be used in [[Tailoring]]. Can be produced by [[Fish Pond]]s.}}\n{{History|1.5|Added Tiger Slime Eggs.}}\n\n{{NavboxAnimals}}\n\n[[Category:Special items]]\n\n[[de:Schleim-Ei]]\n[[es:Huevo de baba]]\n[[fr:Oeuf de Slime]]\n[[it:Uovo di melma]]\n[[ja:スライムのタマゴ]]\n[[ko:슬라임 알]]\n[[hu:Ragacstojás]]\n[[pt:Ovo de gosma]]\n[[ru:Яйцо слайма]]\n[[tr:Balçıkça Yumurtası]]\n[[zh:史莱姆蛋]]"
    }
